{"data":[{"id":559455803,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"01da282cd54fa04dc75643944d8b43bb","url_token":"gao-san-gou-67-76","name":"肖明浩BIT","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04af9d8966ecf44558e55a787b6ab92f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-04af9d8966ecf44558e55a787b6ab92f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/01da282cd54fa04dc75643944d8b43bb","user_type":"people","headline":"略带低级趣味的理工男","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":3198,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559455803","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545728379,"updated_time":1545908915,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":55,"comment_count":15,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我先在这里mark一下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e按照我的能力，我是没资格来谈论哥德巴赫猜想的证明的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想说几句别的:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果题主身为一个高中生拥有证明哥德巴赫猜想的能力的话，我想你不必现在还在纠结会不会被清北的数院保送的问题。你现在应该已经可以拿到IMO金牌了吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对了最后补充一句，T大的数院不如P大的。如果是真的，去MIT都是屈才。所以我推荐你去中科大，和贱贱老师 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/789a006980ffe4e7d86594fd2c21c927\" data-hash=\"789a006980ffe4e7d86594fd2c21c927\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$789a006980ffe4e7d86594fd2c21c927\"\u003e@贱贱\u003c/a\u003e 称兄道弟。我也推荐你去山东某世界一流大学（副部级）的泰山学堂，世一大（副部级）的数学系全国知名，你值得拥有。详情请咨询邓总 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47ac97a287b10d41ef3239f61ea08920\" data-hash=\"47ac97a287b10d41ef3239f61ea08920\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$47ac97a287b10d41ef3239f61ea08920\"\u003e@邓铂鋆\u003c/a\u003e （狗头保命）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是我觉得这是假的，我把话放在哪里这里，欢迎明年1月1日来打脸。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对了，论文发在知乎上面你不觉得太可惜了吗？不得发在微博这种用户更多的平台吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，我严肃说一下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我希望以后不要在知乎上看见这种问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53405629\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-18a4e4f21513c06dc69b04d807afbccf_r.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1034\" data-image-height=\"1128\" class=\"internal\"\u003e肖明浩BIT：民科还是天才，这是一个问题\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我先在这里mark一下:按照我的能力，我是没资格来谈论哥德巴赫猜想的证明的。我想说几句别的:如果题主身为一个高中生拥有证明哥德巴赫猜想的能力的话，我想你不必现在还在纠结会不会被清北的数院保送的问题。你现在应该已经可以拿到IMO金牌了吧？对了最后补…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge